  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5306524/" class="title-link">天地有大美而不言</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5306524"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/yanzhige/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u13408164-26.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/yanzhige/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">胭脂冷</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-02-15"
      class="main-meta">2012-02-15 16:44:59</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5306524_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  这是一本让人惊艳的书，它像一首长诗一样，以自己独特的方式歌颂了自然的美好与丰富，庄严与神奇。在一个春寒未消的午后，它带我进入17世纪末到19世纪末的那些浪漫的人类探险之旅，跟随着航向牙买加的船队，转而探索锡兰，漫游北美洲，横跨太平洋……在汉斯.斯隆爵士、保罗.赫...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/5306524/#comments">(13回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">31有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5306524_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5306524_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










            <p class="pl" align="right">
                &gt;
                <a href="reviews">
                    更多书评43篇
                </a>
            </p>
</section>
    
